<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Section</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="path/to/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-DTOQO9RWCH3ppGqcWaEA1BIZOC6xxalwEsw9c2QQeAIftl+Vegovlnee1c9QX4TctnWMn13TZye+giMm8e2LwA==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <style>
        .contact-section-contacUs {
            margin-left: 20%;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }

        .contact-info, .contact-form {
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

            .contact-form button {
                background-color: #007bff; /* Bootstrap primary blue */
                color: white;
                border-radius: 25px;
                border: none;
                padding: 10px 20px;
            }

        .form-control {
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .contact-form button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3; /* Darker blue on hover */
        }

        .contact-info div, .contact-info a {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .contact-icons {
            font-size: 24px; /* Adjust icon size as needed */
            color: #007bff; /* Bootstrap primary blue */
        }

            .contact-icons a {
                margin: 0 10px;
            }

        .custom-image-icons {
            width: 25px;
            height: 25px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class=" contact-section-contacUs">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <h2>Bize Ulaşın</h2>
                <p>Hoş geldiniz! Eğer herhangi bir sorunuz, öneriniz ya da işbirliği tekli  finiz varsa, sizinle iletişim kurmaktan memnuniyet duyarız.</p>
                <div class="contact-info d-flex flex-column">
                    <div style="display:flex">
                        <img src="~/images/1.png" alt="1" class="custom-image-icons">
                        <img src="~/images/2.png" alt="1" class="custom-image-icons">
                        <img src="~/images/3.png" alt="1" class="custom-image-icons">
                        <img src="~/images/4.png" alt="1" class="custom-image-icons">
                        <img src="~/images/5.png" alt="1" class="custom-image-icons">
                        <img src="~/images/6.png" alt="1" class="custom-image-icons">
                    </div>

                    <div class="contact-icons mt-3">
                        <i style="color:#0c0f12;background-color:#f4f4f4" class="fa-brands fa-facebook-f"></i>
                        <i style="color:#0c0f12;background-color:#f4f4f4" class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i>
                        <i style="color:#0c0f12;background-color:#f4f4f4" class="fa-brands fa-square-twitter"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-6" style="width:500px;">
                <form class="contact-form">
                    <div class="row mb-3">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <label style="font-weight:500">İsim Soyisim</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Yazınız...">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <label style="font-weight:500">Email Adresi</label>
                            <input type="email" class="form-control" placeholder="Yazınız...">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row mb-3">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <label style="font-weight:500">Telefon </label>
                            <input type="tel" class="form-control" placeholder="Yazınız...">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <label style="font-weight:500">Konu </label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Yazınız...">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <textarea class="form-control" rows="5" placeholder="Lütfen buraya mesajınızı yazınız..."></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send Message</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
